        <abstract> 
<p>CD sends thanks for <hi rend="italic">Manual of European butterflies</hi> [1862].</p> 
            <p>Is pleased that WFK does not believe in immutability of species, "a doctrine perfectly adapted to stop philosophical research", and hopes he will publish further.</p>
            <p>Notes WFK’s name is the same as the entomologist’s.</p>
        </abstract>
